This paper discusses the use of blockchain technology for business management, which involves security and distributed computing aspects, suggesting that it could belong to the categories of Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Software Engineering (cs.SE), Databases (cs.DB), and Cybersecurity (cs.CY).
